        "creation_date": 1433407012,
        "body": "<p>For servlet url mapping, you have to use <code>&lt;url-pattern&gt;/&lt;/url-pattern&gt;<\/code> instead of <code>&lt;url-pattern&gt;/*&lt;/url-pattern&gt;<\/code>, because <code>/*<\/code> overrides the default JspServlet mapping. You can find more details about difference between <code>/<\/code> and <code>/*<\/code> at this <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/4140448/difference-between-and-in-servlet-mapping-url-pattern\">answer<\/a><\/p>\n",
        "answer_id": 30638917,
        "question_id": 30625167,
        "last_edit_date": 1495540268
    }],
